{"tid":1849172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解最近幾日少左好多中國國內有關武漢肺炎既消息？","createTime":"2020-01-29T01:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T17:09:22.000Z","uid":254729,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"873ab4a5879428bd4bdd6b8b4f38127eb3105047","tid":1849172,"uid":254729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"因為國內又開始禁言維穩啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bGXAMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bGXAMi.png&h=7e7ea84a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PaNDkc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPaNDkc0.jpg&h=d7376386&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMDyTx1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMDyTx1.jpg&h=9551f56e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amzx86n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Famzx86n.jpg&h=64417399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家Twitter 仲有少少中國人會講下近況<br />\n強烈推薦大家用twitter"},{"pid":"d484000f2e7dedca68eb10997135700f98fcfe92","tid":1849172,"uid":254729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4t7WRk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4t7WRk6.jpg&h=8cc86dbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"733538db5b682e486ef19cb87a17dacffcf09afb","tid":1849172,"uid":313312,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"（取笑系列）抗爭者真係好垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ce067e5c4cff729ee20703b2a1150bb30b9100f","tid":1849172,"uid":76310,"like